## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not include the most recent research findings or policy changes. Additionally, while the sources used are reputable, the complexity of climate systems means that new discoveries could alter current understandings. The report focuses on human activities and does not extensively cover natural factors influencing climate change.